Comment (src/views/admin/NotificationsView.vue:1097):
`sendTestNotification()` uses a single `testSendLoadingKey` for all destinations. If multiple test sends are triggered before the first finishes, the loading state and final toast/message can be cleared/overwritten by the earlier request finishing. Consider tracking loading state per destination (e.g., a Set/Map of keys or a request sequence per key) so concurrent sends don’t interfere.
